title: Win The War Within | Joel Osteen

description:
Everyday, we have to make the choice between settling or doing the right thing. That discomfort you feel is a sign that God is calling you higher.

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
